<p>We control your personal data on our mobile applications and other applications that facilitate Our Services. Please submit any questions, concerns or comments you have about this privacy policy or any requests concerning your personal data by email to help@tix.id or write to us to SCTV Tower Lantai 14, Jl. Asia Afrika Lot. 19, Jakarta Pusat.</p>


